      <title>桌宠对话API使用文档</title>
      <link href="/article/40287.html"/>
      <url>/article/40287.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="智能语音对话系统使用文档"><a href="#智能语音对话系统使用文档" class="headerlink" title="智能语音对话系统使用文档"></a>智能语音对话系统使用文档</h1><h2 id="概述"><a href="#概述" class="headerlink" title="概述"></a>概述</h2><p>本系统提供端到端的智能语音对话能力，整合语音识别(ASR)、大语言模型(LLM)和语音合成(TTS)技术，支持通过API实现完整的语音交互流程。</p><h2 id="快速开始"><a href="#快速开始" class="headerlink" title="快速开始"></a>快速开始</h2><h3 id="环境要求"><a href="#环境要求" class="headerlink" title="环境要求"></a>环境要求</h3><ul><li>Python 3.9+</li><li>FFmpeg (需加入系统PATH)</li><li>依赖库安装：<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">pip install fastapi uvicorn websockets pygame python-multipart fish-audio-sdk pyyaml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ul><h3 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h3><p>在项目根目录创建<code>config.yml</code>：</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">app:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_api_key&quot;</span>  <span class="comment"># 服务端API密钥</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">xunfei:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">app_id:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_xunfei_app_id&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_xunfei_api_key&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">patch_id:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_patch_id&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">fish_audio:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">api_key:</span> <span class="string">&quot;your_fish_audio_key&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">server:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">host:</span> <span class="string">&quot;0.0.0.0&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">port:</span> <span class="number">8000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="启动服务"><a href="#启动服务" class="headerlink" title="启动服务"></a>启动服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">uvicorn main:app --reload</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="API接口说明"><a href="#API接口说明" class="headerlink" title="API接口说明"></a>API接口说明</h2><h3 id="1-语音对话接口"><a href="#1-语音对话接口" class="headerlink" title="1. 语音对话接口"></a>1. 语音对话接口</h3><p><strong>端点</strong><br><code>POST /dialogue_tts/</code></p><p><strong>请求头</strong></p><figure class="highlight http"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attribute">X-API-Key</span><span class="punctuation">: </span>your_api_key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>请求格式</strong><br>Form-data格式：</p><ul><li>mp3_file: 语音文件(MP3格式)</li><li>reference_id: (可选)参考音频ID</li></ul><p><strong>响应示例</strong><br>成功：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;file_path&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;/static/output_1a2b3c4d.mp3&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>错误：</p><figure class="highlight json"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#123;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">&quot;detail&quot;</span><span class="punctuation">:</span> <span class="string">&quot;错误描述&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="punctuation">&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>状态码</strong>  </p><ul><li>200: 处理成功</li><li>401: API密钥无效</li><li>400: 无效的请求参数</li><li>500: 内部处理错误</li><li>503: 第三方服务不可用</li></ul><h3 id="2-文件清理接口"><a href="#2-文件清理接口" class="headerlink" title="2. 文件清理接口"></a>2. 文件清理接口</h3><p><strong>端点</strong><br><code>DELETE /clean_file/&#123;filename&#125;</code></p><p><strong>请求示例</strong></p><figure class="highlight http"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">DELETE /clean_file/output_1a2b3c4d.mp3</span><br><span class="line"><span class="attribute">X-API-Key</span><span class="punctuation">: </span>your_api_key</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>该接口用于清除生成的音频文件</p><h2 id="使用示例"><a href="#使用示例" class="headerlink" title="使用示例"></a>使用示例</h2><h3 id="Python调用示例"><a href="#Python调用示例" class="headerlink" title="Python调用示例"></a>Python调用示例</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">import</span> requests</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">url = <span class="string">&quot;http://localhost:8000/dialogue_tts/&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">headers = &#123;<span class="string">&quot;X-API-Key&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;your_api_key&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">with</span> <span class="built_in">open</span>(<span class="string">&quot;input.mp3&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;rb&quot;</span>) <span class="keyword">as</span> f:</span><br><span class="line">    files = &#123;<span class="string">&quot;mp3_file&quot;</span>: f&#125;</span><br><span class="line">    response = requests.post(url, files=files, headers=headers)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">print</span>(response.json())</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="cURL示例"><a href="#cURL示例" class="headerlink" title="cURL示例"></a>cURL示例</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">curl -X POST <span class="string">&quot;http://localhost:8000/dialogue_tts/&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  -H <span class="string">&quot;X-API-Key: your_api_key&quot;</span> \</span><br><span class="line">  -F <span class="string">&quot;mp3_file=@input.mp3&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="系统架构"><a href="#系统架构" class="headerlink" title="系统架构"></a>系统架构</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">graph TD</span><br><span class="line">    A[用户上传语音] --&gt; B[ASR语音识别]</span><br><span class="line">    B --&gt; C[讯飞大模型处理]</span><br><span class="line">    C --&gt; D[TTS语音合成]</span><br><span class="line">    D --&gt; E[返回语音响应]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="注意事项"><a href="#注意事项" class="headerlink" title="注意事项"></a>注意事项</h2><ol><li><strong>文件管理</strong></li></ol><ul><li>系统自动清理10分钟前的生成文件</li><li>立即清理请使用<code>/clean_file</code>接口</li><li>静态文件存储在<code>/static</code>目录</li></ul><ol start="2"><li><strong>音频格式要求</strong></li></ol><ul><li>输入：MP3格式，16kHz采样率</li><li>输出：MP3格式，24kHz采样率</li></ul><ol start="3"><li><strong>性能指标</strong></li></ol><ul><li>平均响应时间：&lt;5秒</li><li>最大并发数：10请求&#x2F;秒</li></ul><ol start="4"><li><strong>依赖服务</strong></li></ol><ul><li>科大讯飞大模型服务</li><li>Fish-Audio语音服务</li></ul><h2 id="错误排查"><a href="#错误排查" class="headerlink" title="错误排查"></a>错误排查</h2><table><thead><tr><th>错误现象</th><th>可能原因</th><th>解决方案</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>401 Unauthorized</td><td>API密钥错误</td><td>检查请求头X-API-Key配置</td></tr><tr><td>空文件响应</td><td>输入文件损坏</td><td>验证音频文件完整性</td></tr><tr><td>输出语音不完整</td><td>TTS服务超时</td><td>重试请求，检查网络连接</td></tr><tr><td>500 Internal Error</td><td>服务配置错误</td><td>检查config.yml配置完整性</td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="开发指南"><a href="#开发指南" class="headerlink" title="开发指南"></a>开发指南</h2><h3 id="扩展功能"><a href="#扩展功能" class="headerlink" title="扩展功能"></a>扩展功能</h3><ol><li><p>支持更多音频格式：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 在process_audio接口中添加格式转换逻辑</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">from</span> pydub <span class="keyword">import</span> AudioSegment</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">audio = AudioSegment.from_file(input_path)</span><br><span class="line">audio.export(<span class="string">&quot;converted.wav&quot;</span>, <span class="built_in">format</span>=<span class="string">&quot;wav&quot;</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>添加对话历史：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># 修改讯飞请求参数</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">&quot;payload&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="string">&quot;message&quot;</span>: &#123;</span><br><span class="line">        <span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span>: [</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;<span class="string">&quot;role&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;user&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;历史对话1&quot;</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;<span class="string">&quot;role&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;assistant&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;历史回复1&quot;</span>&#125;,</span><br><span class="line">            &#123;<span class="string">&quot;role&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;user&quot;</span>, <span class="string">&quot;content&quot;</span>: <span class="string">&quot;当前问题&quot;</span>&#125;</span><br><span class="line">        ]</span><br><span class="line">    &#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li></ol><h2 id="版权声明"><a href="#版权声明" class="headerlink" title="版权声明"></a>版权声明</h2><p>本系统基于以下技术构建：</p><ul><li>FastAPI框架</li><li>科大讯飞开放平台</li><li>Fish-Audio开源项目</li></ul><p>严禁用于任何违法用途，最终解释权归系统所有者所有。</p>]]></content>
      
      
